{"TopicId":152966,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Increase terrain scatter load distance?","CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-04T07:29:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-04T07:29:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003EI hope this is in the right thread. I wasn\u0027t too sure.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi all! Is there a way to increase distance that the Terrain Scatter loads? I want to be able to see the trees from further away. Thanks,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBenji13.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-04T15:08:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck the settings in the main menu. You\u0027ll probably\u00A0find what you\u0027re looking for there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-05T08:15:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222874741\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480864088\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022170752\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gianni1122\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Gianni1122 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck the settings in the main menu. You\u0027ll probably\u00A0find what you\u0027re looking for there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat lets you change the density of the terrain scatter, but not the load distance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-05T16:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222875747\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480925725\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298962\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Streetwind\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Streetwind said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat lets you change the density of the terrain scatter, but not the load distance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh I see. My mistake\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Palaceviking","CreatedById":166883,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-05T17:36:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSry but it\u0027s not minecraft, render distances are not adjustable \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-05T18:11:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Emight\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Ebe a way to alter this in the Settings.cfg but I\u0027m not familiar enough to confirm it. \u003Cem\u003EIF\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0there is a way to increase terrain scatter distance,\u00A0I imagine that\u0027s where you\u0027d find it. You could try finding a mod for it as\u00A0it is possible someone has made one. If all else fails, you can request that a mod author create it in the Add On Discussions.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}